{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Overview</h2>Outerra World Sandbox lets you play and create the world that you want.  It uses multiple data sources to populate the earth\u2019s terrain, roads, buildings, forests, and waterways.  It\u2019s up to you to see where it goes from there.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Explore</h2>Walk, Drive, Sail, Fly or Freecam to anywhere on earth.  <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/575020/extras/train.gif?t=1731387309\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>  The peak of Everest<br></li><li>  The deepest depths of the Mariana Trench<br></li><li>  The Sahara Desert</li></ul>If it is a place on earth that's on your bucket list, you can go there. Plan your dream trip hopping between multiple vehicles across different terrain types. Enjoy the vistas, from land, sea, and sky.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Create</h2>Mold the world following a fantasy or a serious project you have in mind.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/575020/extras/ows1.gif?t=1731387309\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>  Refine the terrain,  and place structures<br></li><li>  Import Vehicles, structures, and other assets<br></li><li>  Import hi-res terrain imagery insets and elevation insets</li></ul><br>Do you want to walk the streets of Paris in the 1930s? Or maybe sculpt New York City at the turn of the 20th century? You can even reimagine landscapes of the earth before they were developed by humankind.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Share</h2>Share your creations via the steam workshop and contribute to an ever-changing world with your own vision.","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/575020/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1731387309","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/575020/page.bg.jpg?t=1731387309","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_a